om the 'twisties'.\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999517475453443, \"rank\": 4.677499801464232e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999991905923344, \"rank\": 8.094083520736845e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9980581958933699, \"rank\": 0.0019455318732865537, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this title\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'twisties\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles produced a sensational display in the Paris event, becoming the oldest winner of her sport's blue-riband event for 72 years.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.561198051771846e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"a sensational display\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest winner\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport's blue-riband event\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"72 years\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 553}]}, {\"sen